---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout 
  title="About Yilong | 30+ Years Medical Scrubs Manufacturer" 
  description="Anhui Yilong Environmental Protection Technology Co., Ltd. - 30+ years of medical scrubs manufacturing. ISO 9001/14001/45001 certified. OEKO-TEX certified. SGS verified factory. OEM/ODM for global healthcare brands."
  keywords="medical scrubs manufacturer, OEM/ODM scrub factory, ISO 9001 hospital uniform supplier, China scrub manufacturer"
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-slate-900 text-white py-16 md:py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1 bg-secondary/20 border border-secondary/30 text-secondary text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest rounded-full mb-4">30+ Years Manufacturing Heritage · Anhui, China</div>
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-4">About <span class="text-secondary">Yilong</span></h1>
      <p class="text-slate-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">30 years of precision manufacturing. One obsession: medical scrubs. OEKO-TEX® certified. ISO 9001/14001/45001 certified. Serving brands, hospitals, and distributors in 60+ countries.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Stats Bar -->
  <section class="bg-slate-900 border-t border-slate-800">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 divide-x divide-slate-800">
        <div class="py-8 md:py-10 text-center px-4">
          <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-secondary mb-1">30+</div>
          <p class="text-[10px] md:text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Years Manufacturing</p>
        </div>
        <div class="py-8 md:py-10 text-center px-4">
          <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-secondary mb-1">60+</div>
          <p class="text-[10px] md:text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Countries Served</p>
        </div>
        <div class="py-8 md:py-10 text-center px-4">
          <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-secondary mb-1">100%</div>
          <p class="text-[10px] md:text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Pre-Shipment QC</p>
        </div>
        <div class="py-8 md:py-10 text-center px-4">
          <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-secondary mb-1">10 Sets</div>
          <p class="text-[10px] md:text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Low MOQ · Ships Worldwide</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Brand Story: Lei Jun Style -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest rounded-full mb-6">Our Story</div>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-8 text-slate-900">One Product. One Obsession.</h2>
        
        <div class="space-y-5 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-base md:text-lg">
          <p>I'm going to be straight with you.</p>
          
          <p>Our manufacturing journey started over 30 years ago. Anhui Yilong Environmental Protection Technology Co., Ltd. was established in 2017 — purpose-built to focus entirely on the medical scrubs category.</p>

<p>We don't chase trends. We don't scatter our resources. We go deep, not wide.</p>
          
          <p>The garment industry is full of factories that chase margins. One month they're making scrubs, next month they're making workwear, six months later they're making sportswear. Every time they switch products, they lose expertise. The result: inconsistent quality, dropped standards, and buyers who get burned.</p>
          
          <p>We watched it happen. We decided not to do it.</p>
          
          <p>Instead, we put everything — every R&D dollar, every production line, every QC inspection — into one product. 30 years of refinement. The result is a fabric formula we can stand behind, a production process we can explain, and quality we can guarantee in writing.</p>
          
          <p class="bg-secondary/5 border-l-4 border-secondary p-6 rounded-r-2xl text-slate-700 not-italic font-medium">
            <strong class="text-secondary">Same fabric. Same QC. The only difference is the order quantity.</strong>
          </p>
          
          <p>Whether you're ordering 10 sets for your first private label run, or 10,000 sets for a hospital group contract — you get the same fabric, the same 100% pre-shipment inspection, the same OEKO-TEX certified materials.</p>
          
          <p>And if something is wrong with your order? We'll fix it. We have a track record to protect, and 60+ countries are watching.</p>
          
          <div class="pt-4 border-t border-slate-200">
            <p class="text-slate-500 italic">No BS. No bait and switch. Just good scrubs, honestly made.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Choose Us -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-12 md:mb-16">
        <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-slate-200 text-slate-600 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest rounded-full mb-4">Why Yilong</div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-black text-slate-900">Why 60+ Countries Choose Yilong</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-500 mt-3">Numbers don't lie. SGS tested. Third-party verified.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 md:gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-4">🏭</div>
          <h3 class="font-black text-lg mb-3 text-slate-900">30+ Years of Focus</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">30 years of manufacturing expertise, with medical scrubs as our core focus.</p>
          <div class="space-y-1">
            <div class="flex justify-between text-xs text-slate-500 border-t border-slate-100 pt-2">
              <span>Founded</span><span class="font-bold text-slate-700">1994</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between text-xs text-slate-500">
              <span>Product categories</span><span class="font-bold text-slate-700">Medical Scrubs Only</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-4">🧪</div>
          <h3 class="font-black text-lg mb-3 text-slate-900">72/21/7 Premium Fabric</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">205 GSM high-density 4-way stretch fabric. OEKO-TEX® Standard 100 certified. Formulated for FIGs-quality feel at a competitive price.</p>
          <div class="space-y-1 text-xs text-slate-500 border-t border-slate-100 pt-2">
            <div class="flex justify-between"><span>Color fastness</span><span class="font-bold text-slate-700">Grade 4-5 / 5 (SGS tested)</span></div>
            <div class="flex justify-between"><span>Shrinkage</span><span class="font-bold text-slate-700">&lt;0.5% (SGS tested)</span></div>
            <div class="flex justify-between"><span>Wash durability</span><span class="font-bold text-slate-700">40+ cycles (SGS tested)</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-4">🦠</div>
          <h3 class="font-black text-lg mb-3 text-slate-900">Antibacterial & Functional</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">Optional silver-ion antibacterial finishing. Lab verified &gt;99.9% reduction against E. coli, S. aureus, and C. albicans (SGS tested per AATCC 100-2019).</p>
          <div class="space-y-1 text-xs text-slate-500 border-t border-slate-100 pt-2">
            <div class="flex justify-between"><span>E. coli reduction</span><span class="font-bold text-slate-700">&gt;99.9%</span></div>
            <div class="flex justify-between"><span>S. aureus reduction</span><span class="font-bold text-slate-700">&gt;99.9%</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-4">📦</div>
          <h3 class="font-black text-lg mb-3 text-slate-900">Small Brand Friendly MOQ</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">Color MOQ from 10 sets/color. Sizes can be freely mixed within each color. Logo customization from 20 sets/style. Industry norm is 50–200 sets/color.</p>
          <p class="text-xs font-bold text-secondary">You bring the design. We handle the rest.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-4">🎨</div>
          <h3 class="font-black text-lg mb-3 text-slate-900">7 Logo Branding Methods</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">Embroidery, screen printing, heat transfer, DTG, foil stamping, pad printing, sublimation — one-stop-shop for all your branding needs.</p>
          <p class="text-xs font-bold text-secondary">Custom packaging also available.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-4">🌍</div>
          <h3 class="font-black text-lg mb-3 text-slate-900">DDP Shipping Worldwide</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">Sea freight, air freight, and express. DDP service (freight + customs + duties included) for USA, Canada, Mexico, LATAM, and the Middle East.</p>
          <p class="text-xs font-bold text-secondary">No surprise fees at delivery.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Certifications: Full Three-System ISO + OEKO-TEX + SGS -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white border-t border-slate-100">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-green-100 text-green-700 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest rounded-full mb-4">Certifications</div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-4">Trust Built on Evidence</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-500 max-w-xl mx-auto">Every certification is real, current, and verifiable. We include certificate numbers so your procurement team can confirm directly.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- ISO Three-System -->
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-10">
        <h3 class="font-black text-lg mb-1 text-slate-900">ISO Management System Certifications</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mb-6">Issued by Beijing NGV Certification Center ( accredited by CNCA )</p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-5">
          <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-blue-200">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center font-black text-sm">ISO</div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-black text-slate-900 text-sm">ISO 9001:2015</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-blue-600">Quality Management System</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-2 text-xs">
              <div class="flex justify-between"><span class="text-slate-500">Certificate No.</span><span class="font-bold text-slate-700">05326Q00153R101</span></div>
              <div class="flex justify-between"><span class="text-slate-500">Valid until</span><span class="font-bold text-slate-700">March 2029</span></div>
              <div class="flex justify-between"><span class="text-slate-500">Scope</span><span class="font-bold text-slate-700">Medical apparel manufacturing</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-green-50 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-green-200">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-green-600 text-white rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center font-black text-sm">ISO</div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-black text-slate-900 text-sm">ISO 14001:2015</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-green-600">Environmental Management System</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-2 text-xs">
              <div class="flex justify-between"><span class="text-slate-500">Certificate No.</span><span class="font-bold text-slate-700">05326E00122R101</span></div>
              <div class="flex justify-between"><span class="text-slate-500">Valid until</span><span class="font-bold text-slate-700">March 2029</span></div>
              <div class="flex justify-between"><span class="text-slate-500">Scope</span><span class="font-bold text-slate-700">Eco-friendly production process</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-orange-50 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-orange-200">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-orange-500 text-white rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center font-black text-sm">ISO</div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-black text-slate-900 text-sm">ISO 45001:2018</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-orange-500">Occupational Health & Safety</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-2 text-xs">
              <div class="flex justify-between"><span class="text-slate-500">Certificate No.</span><span class="font-bold text-slate-700">05326S00118R101</span></div>
              <div class="flex justify-between"><span class="text-slate-500">Valid until</span><span class="font-bold text-slate-700">March 2029</span></div>
              <div class="flex justify-between"><span class="text-slate-500">Scope</span><span class="font-bold text-slate-700">Workplace safety systems</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- OEKO-TEX + SGS -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-200">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-5">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-green-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-black">✓</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-black text-lg text-slate-900">OEKO-TEX® Standard 100</h3>
              <p class="text-xs text-green-600 font-bold">Fabric Safety Certified</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">Every fabric batch independently tested for harmful substances by OEKO-TEX® authorized laboratory. Safe for prolonged skin contact in healthcare environments.</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">Certificate available upon bulk order request.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-200">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-5">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-red-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-black">SGS</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-black text-lg text-slate-900">SGS Factory Verification</h3>
              <p class="text-xs text-red-600 font-bold">On-Site Verified · December 2025</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">Third-party audited manufacturing facility. Production capacity, quality systems, and labor standards verified by SGS — the world's leading inspection and testing company.</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">SGS verification report available upon request.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Who We Serve -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest rounded-full mb-4">Who We Serve</div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-8 text-slate-900">Our Clients</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 bg-white rounded-xl p-5 border border-slate-200">
            <span class="text-2xl flex-shrink-0">🇺🇸</span>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">US/Canada D2C Brands</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Private label programs, ecommerce sellers, direct-to-consumer scrub brands targeting the North American market.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 bg-white rounded-xl p-5 border border-slate-200">
            <span class="text-2xl flex-shrink-0">🏥</span>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Hospital Groups & Nursing Homes</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Large-scale institutional orders. ISO 9001/45001 certified supplier for hospital procurement and government tenders.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 bg-white rounded-xl p-5 border border-slate-200">
            <span class="text-2xl flex-shrink-0">🏪</span>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Wholesale Distributors</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Reliable supply partners for medical apparel distributors across Europe, Middle East, and Asia Pacific.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 bg-white rounded-xl p-5 border border-slate-200">
            <span class="text-2xl flex-shrink-0">🏨</span>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Medical Clinic Chains</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Dental clinics, aesthetic clinics, pediatric practices, and specialty medical chains requiring consistent uniform programs.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 bg-white rounded-xl p-5 border border-slate-200 sm:col-span-2">
            <span class="text-2xl flex-shrink-0">👩‍⚕️</span>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Micro-Brand Entrepreneurs</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Nurses and healthcare professionals building their own brands from scratch. Low MOQ, hands-on support. Most of our US clients started exactly like this.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Markets -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-slate-900 text-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-secondary/20 border border-secondary/30 text-secondary text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest rounded-full mb-6">30 years. 60+ countries. One product.</div>
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-4">Serving 60+ Countries Across 6 Continents</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 mt-10">
        <span class="px-5 py-2 bg-slate-800 rounded-full text-slate-300">🇺🇸 North America</span>
        <span class="px-5 py-2 bg-slate-800 rounded-full text-slate-300">🇪🇺 Europe</span>
        <span class="px-5 py-2 bg-slate-800 rounded-full text-slate-300">🇸🇦 Middle East</span>
        <span class="px-5 py-2 bg-slate-800 rounded-full text-slate-300">🌏 Southeast Asia</span>
        <span class="px-5 py-2 bg-slate-800 rounded-full text-slate-300">🌍 Africa</span>
        <span class="px-5 py-2 bg-slate-800 rounded-full text-slate-300">🌎 Latin America</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-secondary text-white text-center">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-4">Ready to Visit Our Factory or Place a Trial Order?</h2>
      <p class="text-emerald-100 max-w-xl mx-auto mb-8">No agents. No middlemen. Factory direct pricing with full quality control. Get your sample quote in 24 hours.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/contact" class="bg-white text-secondary font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-slate-100 transition shadow-lg">Contact Us Today →</a>
        <a href="/products" class="bg-transparent border-2 border-white text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold hover:bg-white/10 transition">View Product Catalog</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
